      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49232,49352,49636,49888,50100</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Albert</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれ？　なんかヘンくね？
さっきまで戦い疲れてたのに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? What's going on around here? The wounds from all those fights are...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体力が回復してる？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our strength has... been recovered?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エッヘヘ～ン！　アルベルト様が教えてやるだーよ。
それも『なりきり士』の力のひとつだ、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ehehe! The great Albert shall teach you! That's yet another of the powers of Roleplayer, &lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン様の加護ある場所なら、
大地の力で体力も全回復だ～～よ♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Miss Norn's divine protection is present in this place, the power of earth will fully recover your inner strength.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえがそんなでけーずーたい隠して、
手伝わないから疲れるんだっての！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're hiding something from us, aren't you? Don't try to act all innocent, it's getting old!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はん、おら、戦ってもええだが、衣装がボロボロになるだど！
偉そうなこと言って。おめぇが使えねぇからだろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know, I might not be doing the fighting, but I'm already tired helping out with clothing! I even tell you guys important information, so I'm certainly more useful than you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、アルベルトさんも……
やめてください</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, Mister Albert... please just cut it out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あう～～ん、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;ぅ、言ってやってほしいだ。
このクソぼうずに、おらがどれだけ大変かっちゅーの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohhhh! &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! Now YOU're one I really want to talk to. It's so difficult to relate with uncivilized people at times!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんのぉ～……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You little...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>っつーことで、ダンジョンから外に出れば、
体力が全快だで、いちいち寝る必要もないだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh that's right, whenever you come out from a dungeon your inner strength will be fully recovered, so there is no need to sleep in inns at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_008_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……誰に向かって
言ってんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Who's he talking to?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
